  "title": "Accounts/Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for an individual to provide accounting and administrative support to our Accounts and HR departments for the group of companies. The responsibilities of this position include generating and processing data entries for invoices and payments related to Accounts Receivable and Accounts Payable.   Additionally, the role will involve handling some HR and administrative tasks, including creating Excel reports.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We seek a candidate who is cheerful, has a positive work attitude, is punctual, and is willing to take on various job responsibilities. We are open to training the right candidates to help them succeed in this role. Poly graduates are encouraged to apply.</p>",
